"\n\nBuffalo, New York, is a major economic and cultural center on the eastern shores of Lake Erie. Home to more than 260,000 people, Buffalo also serves as the home to 30,000 college students. Its bustling downtown offers a vibrant cultural and entertainment scene, diverse shopping and dining opportunities, and proximity to Niagara Falls, one of the seven natural wonders of the world. Buffalo also boasts historic architecture, thriving arts and music scenes, and vibrant neighborhoods."